Package com.common

Interface GatewayInt

All Superinterfaces:
Remote
All Known Implementing Classes:
Gateway
public interface GatewayInt extends Remote
The GatewayInt interface defines remote methods that can be invoked on the Gateway server from a client. Extends the Remote interface, indicating that objects implementing this interface can be invoked remotely.
